question: Chris has three times as many TikTok friends as Joe. Anna has one times as many friends on TikTok as Joe. If Chris has 150 friends on TikTok, how many TikTok friends does Anna have?
answer:
Joe has 150/3 = <<150/3=50>>50 TikTok friends.
Anna has 1*50 = <<1*50=50>>50 TikTok friends.
#### 50
